reviews.comments:
Marcos is great host. Always ready to help, picked us from the train station and provide us full pack of the information about the Barcelona. Also he provided us some discounts and vouchers for Zoo and etc. 
The house is:
- Very convenient location (You can reach the Barceloneta beach, Zoo in 15 minutes by tram);
- Easy to reach by train from the Airport; 
- Glories and Clot metros are around 5-10 minutes, 
- Over the road the big shopping center Glories, with a lot of shops + supermarket + food court;
- Fully equipped with appliances;
- Towels, soaps and etc;  
- Highspeed WLAN;
- Flat is very clean and nice;
 
I will recommend this house and host.
